     A*----------+-----+----------+-----------------------------------*
     A*2021.02.22|DCS. |T.MITSUI  | CHANGE WITH THE NUMBER OF FIGURES *
     A*          |     |          |          EXPANSION OF THE "KANBAN"*
     A*----------+-----+----------+-----------------------------------*
     A*%%EC
     A                                      DSPSIZ(24 80 *DS3)
     A                                      PRINT
     A                                      CF01
     A                                      CF05
     A                                      CF12
     A          R DSP01
     A                                      OVERLAY
     A            #PGM           8   O  1  2
     A                                  1 26'** WASHER TEMPORARY KANBAN **'
     A                                      DSPATR(RI)
     A                                  1 63DATE
     A                                      EDTCDE(Y)
     A                                  1 72TIME
     A                                  5 18'Location code:'
     A                                      DSPATR(HI)
     A            D@LOC1         1   B  5 33DSPATR(CS)
     A            D@LOC2         2   B  5 35DSPATR(CS)
     A            D@LOC3         2   B  5 38DSPATR(CS)
     A            D@LOC4         1   B  5 41DSPATR(CS)
     A                                  7 20'You may type a part of the code.'
     A                                  8 20'If the code is blank, all the loca-
     A                                      tion will be shown.'
     A*
     A          R SFL01                     SFL
     A            S@MAIS         5  0B  5  2DSPATR(CS)
     A                                      EDTCDE(4)
     A  61                                  DSPATR(RI PC)
     A            S@LAST         3A  O  5 10
     A            S@LOC1         1A  O  5 15
     A            S@LOC2         2A  O  5 17
     A            S@LOC3         2A  O  5 20
     A            S@LOC4         1A  O  5 23
